<title type="html"><![CDATA[NSF player for the TurboGrafx]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=6839&amp;p=66025#p66025"><![CDATA[
To eliminate snow, make your screen updates only during VSync or HSync.  To change the screen resolution, of course you have to adjust the dot clock via the VCE ($0400).  The lowest two bits of $0400 control it.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=355">ccovell</a> — Sun Aug 15, 2010 1:49 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
